{
  "texts": [
    "Another field of research concerns the optimization of the variational parameters.",
    "As the number of variational parameters increases, performance of classical optimizers can decrease significantly.",
    "This can be attributed to multiple factors, such as the interaction between noise and large number of parameters, as well as the formation of Barren Plateaus 56.",
    "New ways to optimize such non-linear functions evaluated on quantum computers are currently explored 106.",
    "The first variational algorithm that was employed on a photonic quantum computer is the variational quantum eigensolver (VQE) 107."
  ]
}